transcription.text:
Speaker 1: Hi, thank you for calling Viagra, Escort Blue. How can I help you today?

Speaker 2: Hi, how are you? This is Mario. I was calling you last week.

Speaker 1: I got the refill for my medication on Wednesday I believe,

Speaker 2: and I just wanted to suspend the auto-delivery for a while until May.

Speaker 1: But I don't know if the medicine has already been shipped.

Speaker 2: Let me take a look sir. Could I get your full name and date of birth?

Speaker 1: Yes, Mario Gomez, D-O-M-E-Z, 10-11-1977.

Speaker 2: Okay, so I see the prescription, yes, so that one went through on the 22nd.

Speaker 1: It appears that it's set to be delivered, or was delivered just yesterday at 3 p.m.

Speaker 2: Oh, so I already got it?

Speaker 1: Yeah, it's at 129 West 31st Street.

Speaker 2: Yep.

Speaker 1: Yeah, it said it was dropped off at the front desk reception mail room.

Speaker 2: Now regarding the prescription as a whole, if you want, I can pause it.

Speaker 1: When did you want to pause it for?

Speaker 2: I would say May.

Speaker 1: Yeah, not a problem at all.

Speaker 2: All right, so this has already been charged, right, this delivery, this last prescription?

Speaker 1: This one was correct.

Speaker 2: All right, okay, well I'll just keep it, and why don't we say June then?

Speaker 1: Sure, I can do it to June. Do you want to do June 1st or do you want to do June 31st?

Speaker 2: June 1st is good.

Speaker 1: Okay, you got it.

Speaker 2: All righty.

Speaker 1: All right, you're all set then.

Speaker 2: All right, thank you very much.

Speaker 1: Thank you.

Speaker 2: All right, bye.
